    "body": "### Fixed\n\n- **`login_anthropic()` ΓÇõ loopback redirect_uri ΓÁÈ manual-paste φÔ¿φã┤ Ω╡É∞▓┤.**\n  v0.99.0 ∞ùÉ∞ã£ δÂã∞₧àδÉ£ loopback HTTP server (`http://localhost:54123/callback`)\n  δèõ OAuth client `9d1c250a-ΓÇª` ∞ùÉ δô▒δíÙδÉ£ redirect URI Ω░Ç ∞òãδÍêδÙ╝ authorize\n  δÍ¿Ω│ã∞ùÉ∞ã£ Ω▒░∞áêδÉÉδÍñ (∞é¼∞ÜÒ∞₧É δ│┤Ω│á ΓÇõ δÀÉ δ▓ê ∞Í£δÂã δ¬¿δÀÉ ~50∞┤ê δºÔ∞ùÉ ∞ÍñφÔ¿, auth.toml\n  δ»╕δ│ÇΩ▓╜). Claude Code native binary ∞ÙÌ strings δ╢ã∞ãÙ∞£╝δí£ ∞áòδÍ╡ redirect URI\n  Ω░Ç `https://platform.claude.com/oauth/code/callback` ∞₧ã∞Ùã φÕò∞Ù╕ ΓÇõ ∞ã£δ▓ã ∞╕í\n  callback φÃÌ∞Ù┤∞ºÇΩ░Ç ∞é¼∞ÜÒ∞₧É∞ùÉΩ▓Ô `code#state` φÌò∞ÍÙ∞Ùã φÀ£∞Í£φòÌδÒ┤ ∞é¼∞ÜÒ∞₧ÉΩ░Ç CLI\n  δí£ paste φòÌδèõ manual-paste φÔ¿φã┤. `_run_anthropic_pkce_flow` δÑ╝ 1:1\n  δ»╕δÓ¼δí£ ∞₧¼∞₧À∞ã▒: HTTPServer / `_pick_free_port` / ∞╜£δ░▒ φò╕δôñδÓ¼ ∞á£Ω▒░, paste\n  φÔÔ∞ã£ (`_parse_pasted_code` ΓÇõ URL/fragment/bare code 3 φÌò∞ÍÙ ∞êÌ∞ÜÒ) δÂã∞₧à,\n  scope ∞ùÉ `user:sessions:claude_code` ∞╢õΩ░Ç (binary hint ∞áòφòÒ). Tier 3\n  impersonation ∞áò∞▒à∞ÙÇ Ω╖╕δÔÇδí£.\n\n- **`login_anthropic()` ΓÇõ switched loopback redirect to manual-paste.**\n  v0.99.0's loopback HTTP server (`http://localhost:54123/callback`) was\n  rejected at the authorize step because the OAuth client `9d1c250a-ΓÇª`\n  is registered with only one redirect URI:\n  `https://platform.claude.com/oauth/code/callback` (server-hosted).\n  Confirmed by `strings(8)` analysis of Claude Code's native binary +\n  user reports of two consecutive ~50s failures with no auth.toml write.\n  `_run_anthropic_pkce_flow` rewritten as a 1:1 mirror of Claude Code's\n  manual-paste flow: the loopback HTTP server, port picker, and request\n  handler are removed; a paste parser (`_parse_pasted_code`) accepts the\n  full callback URL, the `code#state` fragment, or the bare code; scope\n  set extended with `user:sessions:claude_code` per the binary's hint\n  string. Tier 3 impersonation posture unchanged."
