    "body": "### Added\n\n- **`core.audit.diagnostics` ΓÇõ file-based diagnostics log surviving\n  `inspect eval` subprocess boundaries.** PR E/F (v0.90.0) ∞ÙÌ ad-hoc\n  `core/_fa4_debug.py` φÔ¿φã┤∞ÙÌ ∞áò∞ÍÙ ∞Ù╕φõãδÙ╝φÕõ. `inspect eval` ∞ÙÌ child\n  process Ω░Ç `subprocess.run(capture_output=True)` δí£ stdout/stderr\n  Ω▓Òδª¼ + inspect_ai ∞ÙÌ `init_logger` Ω░Ç root LogHandler ∞₧¼∞ãñ∞áò ΓÁÈ\n  GEODE plugin ∞ÙÌ INFO/DEBUG Ω░Ç parent δí£ propagate ∞òê δÉ¿. file-based\n  append-only log Ω░Ç ∞Ù┤ δÀÉ boundary ∞ÕÇ δ¼┤Ω┤ÇφòÌΩ▓Ô evidence δ│┤∞í┤.\n  - **API** ΓÇõ `from core.audit import diag, diagnostics_path`.\n    `diag(\"petri.anthropic\", f\"BadRequest: {msg[:200]}\")` φò£ ∞ñãδí£ φÌ╕∞╢£\n  - **Location** ΓÇõ `~/.geode/diagnostics/<YYYY-MM>.log` (∞¢õ rotation).\n    `GEODE_DIAGNOSTICS_LOG=<path>` φÕÌΩ▓╜ δ│Ç∞êÌ override (test/CI fixture\n    ∞ÜÒδÂã)\n  - **Line format** ΓÇõ `<unix_ts:%.3f> <pid> <component> <msg>`. grep/jq\n    ∞╣£φÕõ. `component` δèõ dotted namespace (`petri.runner`,\n    `petri.anthropic`, `petri.lifecycle`)\n  - **Best-effort** ΓÇõ δ¬¿δôá `OSError` swallow. diagnostics Ω░Ç audit Ω╣¿δÒ┤\n    ∞òê δÉ¿ (disk full / permission denied)\n  - **GEODE convention ∞Ù╝Ω┤Ç∞ã▒** ΓÇõ `~/.geode/usage/`, `~/.geode/petri/\n    logs/`, `~/.geode/journal/`, `~/.geode/runs/` ∞ÕÇ Ω░Õ∞ÙÇ ∞£ã∞╣Ì. `/tmp/`\n    Ω░Õ∞ÙÇ OS-level temp ∞òãδÍÌ (PR E/F ∞ÙÌ ∞é¼∞ÜÒ∞₧É δ╣ãφÔÉ δ░Ì∞Ìü)\n  - **φÜÔΩ╖Ç Ω░Çδô£ 10 ∞ÍáΩ╖£** ΓÇõ env override / user expansion / month\n    rotation / DEFAULT_DIAGNOSTICS_DIR ∞╗¿δ▓ñ∞àÌ / write format / append /\n    OSError ∞Ü░φÜÔ / δÂÕ∞Í£ thread write / package re-export / signature\n  - `docs/architecture/petri-observability.md` ∞ÙÌ 3-layer ΓÁÈ **4-layer**\n    φÕò∞₧Ñ (Raw + JSONL ledger + MANIFEST + Diagnostics). Layer 4 ∞ÙÌ\n    `When to reach for` + `Discovery` (grep/awk φÔ¿φã┤) δ¬à∞Í£. 4573\n    passed."
