    "body": "### Fixed\n\n- **Defect B-4 ΓÇõ `inspect_ai` ∞ÙÌ scoring path ∞ÙÌ judge usage\n  δêãδÙ╜ race condition ∞ÙÌ GEODE-∞╕í ∞Ü░φÜÔ fix.** 5/11 8 archives ∞ñÀ 4\n  Ω░£ (~43%) ∞ùÉ∞ã£ judge entry Ω░Ç `stats.role_usage` ∞ùÉ δ»╕δ░Ì∞Ìü.\n  ModelEvent ∞₧É∞▓┤δèõ sample.events ∞ùÉ φò¡∞âü ∞í┤∞₧¼. inspect_ai upstream\n  issue Ω░ÇδèÑ∞ã▒. user-facing Ω▓░Ω│╝: `geode history` ∞ÙÌ judge cost\n  ~43% under-report.\n\n  **fix** ΓÇõ `core/audit/eval_to_jsonl.py` + `core/audit/manifest.py`\n  ∞ÚÀ∞¬╜ event-walk fallback. `eval.model_roles` ∞ùÉ ∞ãá∞Ú╕δÉ£ role ∞Ù┤\n  stats ∞ùÉ∞ã£ missing δ░£Ω▓¼ ΓÁÈ `read_eval_log(path)` (full) δí£ re-read\n  ΓÁÈ `sample.events` ∞ÙÌ `ModelEvent.output.usage` δÑ╝ missing role/\n  model δ│ãδí£ aggregate ΓÁÈ `_SyntheticUsage` δí£ stats dict ∞▒ã∞¢Ç.\n\n  **φÜÔΩ╖Ç Ω░Çδô£ 3 ∞ÍáΩ╖£**:\n  - `test_fallback_recovers_missing_judge_from_events` ΓÇõ race ∞âüφÕÒ\n    ∞₧¼φÌã + fallback ∞Ù┤ role_usage_summary[\"judge\"] δ│╡Ω╡¼\n  - `test_fallback_no_op_when_all_roles_present` ΓÇõ ∞áò∞âü case\n    ∞ÌüφÚÑ ∞ùÁ∞ÙÔ (header_only path Ω╖╕δÔÇδí£)\n  - `test_fallback_logs_warning_when_no_events_match` ΓÇõ events δ╣ã∞Ú┤\n    ∞₧ê∞Ùã δòÔ graceful + WARNING\n\n  **φÜÔΩ╖Ç**: 4563 passed.\n\n  **∞₧õ∞í┤**: B-4 δ│╕∞ºê (inspect_ai scoring race) ∞ÙÇ upstream. GEODE\n  ∞╕í∞ÙÇ δ│╕ fallback δí£ ∞Õã∞áã ∞Ü░φÜÔ ΓÁÈ user-facing δêãδÙ╜ 0%. δÍñ∞ÙÔ audit\n  ∞ùÉ∞ã£ race δ░£∞âÙ ∞Í£ manifest ∞ÙÌ role_usage_summary ∞₧ÉδÂÕ δ│╡Ω╡¼.\n\n### Notes\n\n- **B-1 + B-3 fix ∞₧É∞ù░ Ω▓Ç∞ªÙ δÙ╝∞Ù┤δ╕Ô (anthropic 1 sample, ~$0.25 ∞Íñ∞╕í)\n  + cache hit δ╢Ç∞₧À∞ÜÒ δ░£Ω▓¼.** v0.90.0 (#1024 F-A1+A2+A3) + #1030\n  (B-1 φòÌ∞£ã) + #1031 (B-1 ∞âü∞£ã) + #1034 (B-3) Ω░Ç φò¿Ω╗Ì ∞₧ÀδÂÕφòÌδèõ∞ºÇ\n  Ω▓Ç∞ªÙ. archive `2026-05-11T14-09-15_audit_FAro9bJseFXk2Zk4HpXky9.eval`.\n\n  **Ω▓Ç∞ªÙ contract 4/4 PASS**:\n  - L1 (`.eval` role_usage target non-zero) ΓÇõ `target: in=18 out=873\n    cw=23238 cr=45566`. F-A1 + B-1 fix ∞ÚÀ∞¬╜ ∞₧ÀδÂÕ ∞₧à∞ªÙ\n  - L2 (`~/.geode/usage/` source=\"petri_eval\" 3 rows) ΓÇõ target +\n    judge + auditor + per-call target rows 3\n  - L3 (MANIFEST.jsonl ∞âê line + role_usage_summary) ΓÇõ 13ΓÁÈ14 lines\n  - F-A3/B-3 (LoggerEvent capture) ΓÇõ 6 LoggerEvent (3 turn entry/exit)\n    ∞áòφÕò\n\n  **fa4 ΓÁÈ LoggerEvent ∞áã∞Ù┤**: PR E/F ∞ÙÌ file-based fa4 evidence Ω░Ç\n  PR #1034 ∞ÙÌ namespace setLevel(INFO) fix φ¢ã ∞áò∞ÍÙ `.eval`\n  LoggerEvent δí£ ∞₧ÉδÂÕ ∞è╣Ω▓Ò. text_chars Ω░Ç 924/649/1013 (δ¬¿δÀÉ non-\n  empty) ΓÇõ PR F ∞ÙÌ `apply_messages_cache_control` empty-text guard\n  fix φÜ¿Ω│╝ ∞₧à∞ªÙ.\n\n  **cache hit δ╢Ç∞₧À∞ÜÒ δ░£Ω▓¼**: ∞▓½ ∞Í£δÂãΩ░Ç inspect_ai ∞ÙÌ `~/Library/\n  Caches/inspect_ai/generate/` cache hit ΓÇõ 11s δºÔ∞ùÉ archive ∞âÙ∞ã▒,\n  target usage=None (PR E ∞Ù┤∞áã stale ∞ÙÀδÍ╡). cache clear φ¢ã ∞áò∞âü\n  δÙ╝∞Ù┤δ╕Ô. φÚÑφ¢ã PoC fix Ω▓Ç∞ªÙ ∞Í£ cache clear φòã∞êÌ.\n\n  **δ│╕ Ω▓Ç∞ªÙ cost** target $0.19 + auditor $0.037 + judge $0.018 ΓÊê\n  $0.25, estimator ($0.27) ∞ÕÇ Ω▒░∞ÙÌ ∞Ù╝∞╣Ì.\n\n  **B-4 ∞₧õ∞í┤**: δ│╕ archive ∞ÙÌ judge stats ∞áò∞âü. 8 archives ∞ñÀ PR D\n  1 φÜÔδºÔ δêãδÙ╜. inspect_ai upstream race condition Ω░ÇδèÑ∞ã▒. φ¢ã∞Áì.\n\n  δ│╕ PR ΓÇõ `docs/audits/2026-05-11-petri-observability-audit.md`\n  ┬º9.10 Ω░▒∞Íá (B-3 fixed φÀ£∞Í£) + ∞âê ┬º10 ∞╢õΩ░Ç (Ω▓Ç∞ªÙ Ω▓░Ω│╝) +\n  MANIFEST.jsonl 2 lines ∞₧ÉδÂÕ + summary yaml 2 ∞₧ÉδÂÕ.\n\n### Fixed\n\n- **Defect B-3 ΓÇõ `plugins.petri_audit.*` ∞ÙÌ INFO log Ω░Ç inspect_ai\n  ∞ÙÌ `.eval` LoggerEvent transcript δí£ propagate δÉÌδÂãδíÙ namespace\n  setLevel ∞╢õΩ░Ç.** v0.90.0 ∞Í£∞áÉ PR D/E/F ∞ÙÌ 5 live archives δ¬¿δÀÉ\n  sample LoggerEvent 0 ΓÇõ `_default_geode_runner` ∞ÙÌ `log.info(\"petri\n  runner entry: ...\")` ∞ÕÇ `_response.track_usage` ∞ÙÌ ∞ºãδÍ¿ log Ω░Ç\n  transcript ∞ùÉ ∞òê ∞₧íφ₧Ì.\n\n  **root cause**: Python `logging` ∞ÙÌ effective level chain. inspect_ai\n  `_util/logger.py:init_logger` Ω░Ç root level ∞Ùã ``warning`` (default\n  `DEFAULT_LOG_LEVEL`) ∞£╝δí£ δÀÉΩ│á transcript writer δèõ INFO+ ∞║í∞▓Ì\n  (`DEFAULT_LOG_LEVEL_TRANSCRIPT='info'`). `plugins.petri_audit.*`\n  logger δôñ∞ÙÌ level=NOTSET ΓÁÈ parent chain φÁ╡φò┤ root WARNING ∞£╝δí£\n  fallback ΓÁÈ INFO record Ω░Ç logger δÍ¿Ω│ã∞ùÉ∞ã£ filter out δÉÌ∞Ú┤ root\n  LogHandler ∞ÙÌ emit φÌ╕∞╢£ ∞₧É∞▓┤Ω░Ç ∞ùÁ∞ÙÔ ΓÁÈ LoggerEvent ∞âÙ∞ã▒ ∞òê δÉ¿.\n\n  **fix** (`plugins/petri_audit/__init__.py`):\n  ```python\n  _logging.getLogger(\"plugins.petri_audit\").setLevel(_logging.INFO)\n  ```\n  namespace ∞ÙÌ effective level ∞Ùã INFO δí£ Ω░ò∞á£ ΓÁÈ δ¬¿δôá child logger\n  (`targets.geode_target`, `runner` δô▒) ∞ÙÌ INFO record Ω░Ç process ΓÁÈ\n  propagate=True φÁ╡φò┤ root ∞ÙÌ LogHandler δ░¢∞ÙÔ ΓÁÈ `transcript_levelno\n  >= INFO` ∞▓┤φü¼ φÁ╡Ω│╝ ΓÁÈ `log_to_transcript(record)` φÌ╕∞╢£ ΓÁÈ sample ∞ÙÌ\n  events ∞ùÉ LoggerEvent append.\n\n  **φÜÔΩ╖Ç Ω░Çδô£** (1 ∞ÍáΩ╖£):\n  - `test_petri_audit_namespace_logger_level_is_info` ΓÇõ namespace\n    level=INFO, child `isEnabledFor(INFO)`=True, propagate=True\n    (default ∞£á∞ºÇ) Ω▓Ç∞ªÙ. namespace ∞ÙÌ propagate Ω░Ç False δí£ δ░õδÇÔδÒ┤\n    record Ω░Ç root Ω╣Ô∞ºÇ δ¬╗ Ω░ÇδÍêΩ╣Ô δ¬à∞Í£∞áü guard.\n\n  4522 passed (default env, audit extra φÕÌΩ▓╜∞ùÉ∞ãá 4559). ∞₧É∞ù░ Ω▓Ç∞ªÙ ΓÇõ\n  δÍñ∞ÙÔ audit ∞ÙÌ `.eval` ∞ÙÌ sample.events ∞ùÉ LoggerEvent Ω░Ç non-zero\n  ∞ù¼∞ò╝ φò¿ (petri runner entry/exit + track_usage ∞ÙÌ INFO log)."
