    "body": "> **Cold-start ∞╢õΩ░Ç ΓêÈ53 % (warm median 70 ΓÁÈ 33 ms) via type-only / late-binding lazy.**\n>\n> v0.89.3 δèõ v0.89.2 ∞ÙÌ pydantic / asyncio / importlib.metadata lazy ∞£ã∞ùÉ∞ã£\n> `core.runtime` + `core.wiring.bootstrap` ∞ÙÌ 14+11 Ω░£ type-only import δÑ╝\n> `TYPE_CHECKING` / φò¿∞êÌ-δí£∞╗¼ lazy δí£ ∞╢õΩ░Ç δ╢ãδª¼φò£δÍñ. cold-start\n> `import core.runtime`: **70 ΓÁÈ 33 ms median (warm), 201 ΓÁÈ 167 modules**.\n> v0.89.0 ΓÁÈ v0.89.3 δêã∞áü: cold first-run **240 ΓÁÈ ~33 ms = ΓêÈ86 %**.\n\n### Architecture\n\n- **`core.runtime` + `core.wiring.bootstrap` ∞ÙÌ type-only / late-binding\n  import δÑ╝ cold-start ∞ùÉ∞ã£ ∞á£Ω▒░.**\n  - `core/runtime.py`: 14 Ω░£ φü┤δ₧Ì∞èñ (CUSUMDetector / ExpertPanel /\n    FeedbackLoop / ModelRegistry / OutcomeTracker / SnapshotManager /\n    ContextAssembler / MonoLakeOrganizationMemory / ProjectMemory /\n    ConfigWatcher / TaskGraphHookBridge / TaskGraph / TriggerManager /\n    CorrelationAnalyzer) Ω░Ç dataclass field annotation ∞£╝δí£δºÔ ∞ô░∞₧ã\n    (`from __future__ import annotations` δí£ string φÂÊΩ░Ç) ΓÇõ top-level\n    import ΓÁÈ `if TYPE_CHECKING:` δ╕õδíÙ∞£╝δí£ ∞Ù┤∞áã.\n  - `core/wiring/bootstrap.py`: δÂÕ∞Ù╝ φü┤δ₧Ì∞èñδôñ (ContextAssembler /\n    MonoLake / ProjectMemory / FileBasedUserProfile / ConfigWatcher /\n    RunLog / RunLogEntry / StuckDetector / TaskGraph / TaskGraphHookBridge /\n    InMemorySessionStore) δÂã φò¿∞êÌ-δí£∞╗¼ import δí£ ∞Ù┤∞áã + `TYPE_CHECKING`\n    type stub.  build_* φò¿∞êÌΩ░Ç φÌ╕∞╢£δÉá δòÔδºÔ instantiate.\n  - 5 δ¬¿δôê (`config-lazy` PR φÔ¿φã┤) ∞ÙÌ module-level `settings` alias ∞ÕÇ\n    δÂÕ∞Ù╝φòÌΩ▓Ô `bootstrap.py` ∞ùÉ PEP 562 `__getattr__` ∞╢õΩ░Ç (RunLog /\n    StuckDetector / RunLogEntry) ΓÇõ legacy `patch(\"core.wiring.bootstrap.X\")`\n    φàÔ∞èñφè╕ ∞é¼∞Ù┤φè╕ φÌ╕φÕÌ ∞£á∞ºÇ.\n- ∞╕í∞áò (`import core.runtime`):\n  - v0.89.2 baseline: 54-94 ms warm (median ΓÊê 70 ms), 201 modules\n  - ∞Ù┤ PR: **26-47 ms warm (median ΓÊê 33 ms), 167 modules** = warm\n    median **ΓêÈ37 ms / ΓêÈ53 %** vs v0.89.2.\n  - v0.89.0 ΓÁÈ ∞Ù┤ PR δêã∞áü: cold first-run 240 ΓÁÈ ~33 ms = **ΓêÈ86 %**.\n  - cold-start `sys.modules` ∞ùÉ∞ã£ ∞╢õΩ░Çδí£ δ╣á∞ºÉ: `core.memory.context`,\n    `core.memory.organization`, `core.memory.project`,\n    `core.automation.{drift,feedback_loop,model_registry,outcome_tracking,snapshot,expert_panel}`,\n    `core.scheduler.triggers`, `core.orchestration.{hot_reload,task_bridge,task_system,run_log,stuck_detection}`."
