    "version": "0.89.1",
    "date": "2026-05-09",
    "body": "> **Cold-start ΓêÈ46 % via `core.config` lazy + 19 callsite φò¿∞êÌ-δí£∞╗¼ import.**\n>\n> v0.89.1 ∞ÙÇ cold-start path ∞ÙÌ δ¼┤Ω▒░∞Ü┤ `pydantic_settings` φè╕δª¼ (~150 ms cumulative,\n> 144 modules) δÑ╝ lazy φÕõφò£δÍñ. `core/config.py` (567 lines) δÑ╝ `core/config/`\n> φÔ¿φéñ∞ºÇδí£ δ╢ãδª¼φò┤ `Settings(BaseSettings)` φü┤δ₧Ì∞èñδÑ╝ Ω▓Òδª¼φòÌΩ│á, 19 ∞é¼∞Ù┤φè╕∞ÙÌ\n> top-level `from core.config import settings` ∞Ùã φò¿∞êÌ-δí£∞╗¼ import δí£ ∞Ù┤∞áã.\n> ∞╕í∞áò ΓÇõ `import core.runtime` cold-start: **240 ms ΓÁÈ 128 ms first-run / 80ΓÇô110 ms warm**\n> (median ΓÊê 88 ms) = **ΓêÈ112 ms / ΓêÈ46 %**. 0 regression: 4330 tests pass,\n> E2E A (68.4) unchanged.\n\n### Architecture\n\n- **`core.config` δ¬¿δôê∞Ùã φÔ¿φéñ∞ºÇδí£ δ╢ãδª¼, pydantic_settings φè╕δª¼ lazy φÕõ**\n  (cold-start φÜÔ∞êÌ φÁáδÔÇ). Ω╕░∞í┤ `core/config.py` (567 lines) δÑ╝ `core/config/`\n  φÔ¿φéñ∞ºÇδí£ δ│ÇφÕÌ:\n  - `core/config/_settings.py` (NEW) ΓÇõ `Settings(BaseSettings)` φü┤δ₧Ì∞èñδºÔ Ω▓Òδª¼\n    φòÌ∞ù¼ pydantic / pydantic_settings φÈÇ import φè╕δª¼ (~150 ms cumulative,\n    144 modules) Ω░Ç ∞▓½ settings ∞Ù╕∞èñφã┤∞èñ ∞Üõ∞▓¡ ∞Í£∞áÉΩ╣Ô∞ºÇ δ»╕δñã∞ºÇδÂãδíÙ φò¿.\n  - `core/config/__init__.py` ΓÇõ ∞âü∞êÌ (`*_PRIMARY`, `*_BASE_URL` δô▒),\n    TOML δí£∞ºü, `ModelPolicy`, `RoutingConfig`, `_resolve_provider` δºÔ ∞£á∞ºÇ.\n    `settings` / `Settings` δèõ PEP 562 `__getattr__` δí£ lazy φò┤∞ãÙ.\n- ∞╕í∞áò: `import core.config` δÍ¿δÂà cold = **189 ms ΓÁÈ 34 ms (ΓêÈ82 %)**;\n  modules **308 ΓÁÈ 164**; pydantic_settings Ω░Ç sys.modules ∞ùÉ δôñ∞Ú┤Ω░Ç∞ºÇ\n  ∞òè∞ÙÔ (`settings` ∞▓½ access ∞Í£∞áÉ∞ùÉδºÔ δí£δô£). δÍ¿δÂà∞£╝δí£ cold-start path\n  ∞áã∞▓┤ φÜÔ∞êÌδèõ ∞₧À∞ÙÔ (240 ΓÁÈ 226 ms) ΓÇõ `from core.config import settings`\n  δÑ╝ φò¿∞êÌ-δí£∞╗¼δí£ ∞Ì«Ω╕░δèõ callsite δ│ÇφÕÌ∞Ù┤ δÍñ∞ÙÔ δÍ¿Ω│ã∞ùÉ∞ã£ φò╡∞Í¼ φÜÔ∞êÌδÑ╝ δºÔδôª.\n\n- **`from core.config import settings` ∞ÙÌ cold-start path callsite 19 Ω││∞Ùã\n  φò¿∞êÌ-δí£∞╗¼ import δí£ ∞Ù┤∞áã** (δÍ¿Ω│ã 1 ∞ÙÌ PEP 562 lazy φ¢ã∞Áì). δ│ÇφÕÌ δÔÇ∞âü:\n  - 4-Layer wiring: `core/wiring/{bootstrap,automation,container,startup}.py`\n  - LLM δÙ╝∞Ü░φã░/∞á£Ω│╡∞₧É: `core/runtime.py`, `core/graph.py`,\n    `core/llm/{adapters,fallback,provider_dispatch}.py`,\n    `core/llm/router/calls/{tools,streaming,text,parsed,_failover}.py`,\n    `core/llm/providers/{anthropic,openai,glm}.py`\n  - CLI thin client: `core/cli/{__init__,dispatcher,pipeline_executor,onboarding,\n    welcome,report_renderer}.py`, `core/cli/tool_handlers/system.py`\n  - δÂãδÒõ∞Ù╕ φõÔδÓ¼Ω╖╕∞Ù╕: `plugins/game_ip/cli/batch.py`\n- `core/llm/fallback.py` ∞ÙÌ module-level `MAX_RETRIES` / `RETRY_BASE_DELAY` /\n  `RETRY_MAX_DELAY` (settings ∞ªÊ∞Í£ φÂÊΩ░Ç) δÂã PEP 562 `__getattr__` δí£ lazy\n  φò┤∞ãÙ. `retry_with_backoff_generic` φò¿∞êÌ default δÂã None ∞£╝δí£ δ░õΩ╛╕Ω│á\n  body ∞ùÉ∞ã£ settings ∞ùÉ∞ã£ φò┤∞ãÙ ΓÇõ module load ∞Í£∞áÉ settings φè╕δª¼Ω▒░ ∞░¿δÍ¿.\n- `core/llm/router/__init__.py` ∞ÙÌ `MAX_RETRIES` δô▒ re-export δèõ PEP 562\n  fallback constants lazy δ╢ãΩ╕░δí£ ∞Ù┤∞áã (∞Õ╕δ╢Ç `from core.llm.router import\n  MAX_RETRIES` φÌ╕φÕÌ ∞£á∞ºÇ).\n- 5 δ¬¿δôê (`wiring/{startup,container}`, `cli/onboarding`,\n  `llm/provider_dispatch`, `llm/providers/anthropic`) ∞ùÉ module-level\n  `__getattr__` ∞ÙÌ `settings` lazy alias δÑ╝ ∞╢õΩ░Çφò┤ legacy patch ∞é¼∞Ù┤φè╕\n  (`patch(\"core.X.settings\")`) φÌ╕φÕÌ ∞£á∞ºÇ.\n- ∞ÌüφÚÑ φàÔ∞èñφè╕ (`patch(\"core.X.settings\")` 24 ∞é¼∞Ù┤φè╕) δèõ `core.config.settings`\n  δÍ¿∞Ù╝ patch δí£ φÁ╡∞Ù╝. settings Ω░Ç singleton ∞Ù┤δÙ╝ δÂÕδô▒.\n\n- **∞╕í∞áò (cold-start, `import core.runtime`)**:\n  - v0.89.0 baseline: **240 ms** (single run, clean cache)\n  - δÍ¿Ω│ã 1 (`config` φÔ¿φéñ∞ºÇ δ╢ãδª¼) δÍ¿δÂà: 226 ms (ΓêÈ14 ms / ΓêÈ6 %)\n  - δÍ¿Ω│ã 1+2 φòÒ∞é░ (∞Ù┤ PR): **128 ms cold (first run) / 80ΓÇô110 ms warm\n    (median ΓÊê 88 ms)** ΓÇõ δêã∞áü ΓêÈ112 ms / **ΓêÈ46 %**\n  - `pydantic_settings` / `core.config._settings` Ω░Ç δìõ ∞Ù┤∞âü cold-start ∞ÙÌ\n    `sys.modules` ∞ùÉ δôñ∞Ú┤Ω░Ç∞ºÇ ∞òè∞ÙÔ (∞▓½ settings access ∞Í£∞áÉΩ╣Ô∞ºÇ δ»╕δñã∞ºÉ).\n  - modules count: 382 ΓÁÈ 341 (ΓêÈ41 modules) on cold-start path."
