    "date": "2026-05-09",
    "body": "> **Hardening ΓÇõ `core/graph.py` `# type: ignore[call-overload]` 9 Ω▒┤ ∞á£Ω▒░\n> (B2 batch-3).**  9 Ω░£ langgraph `add_node()` φÌ╕∞╢£∞ÙÌ ignore δ¬¿δÀÉ ∞á£Ω▒░.\n> ∞¢É∞Ù╕: ∞Ü░δª¼ `_node()` wrapper ∞ÙÌ δ░ÌφÕÌ φâÇ∞₧à `Callable[[GeodeState], dict[str, Any]]`\n> ∞Ù┤ langgraph ∞ÙÌ `_Node[NodeInputT_contra]` Protocol Ω│╝ mypy ∞₧à∞₧Ñ∞ùÉ∞ã£\n> ∞₧ÉδÂÕ δºñ∞╣¡δÉÌ∞ºÇ ∞òè∞ÙÔ (mypy Ω░Ç generic Callable ∞Ùã Protocol member δí£\n> ∞₧ÉδÂÕ coerce φòÌ∞ºÇ ∞òè∞ÙÔ).  Solution: ``_node`` ∞ÙÌ δ░ÌφÕÌ∞Ùã langgraph ∞ÙÌ\n> ``_Node[GeodeState]`` Protocol δí£ δ¬à∞Í£ + δ░ÌφÕÌΩ░È∞Ùã `cast()` δí£ localise.\n> 9 Ω░£ ignore ΓÁÈ 0, mypy Ω░Ç `add_node` overload δÑ╝ Ω╣¿δüù∞Ù┤ resolve.\n\n### Changed\n- **`core/graph.py:_node`** ΓÇõ return φâÇ∞₧à `Callable[[GeodeState], dict[str, Any]]` ΓÁÈ `_Node[GeodeState]` (langgraph internal Protocol).  δé┤δ╢Ç∞ùÉ∞ã£ `cast(_Node[GeodeState], _make_hooked_node(...))` / `cast(_Node[GeodeState], fn)` δí£ wrapped/raw fn δ¬¿δÀÉ Protocol δí£ localise.  Runtime δÂÕ∞₧À δ│ÇφÕõ 0 (langgraph δèõ dict-shape return ∞Ùã Ω╖╕δÔÇδí£ δ░¢∞ÙÔ).\n- **9 Ω░£ `add_node` φÌ╕∞╢£ (line 514ΓÇô522)** ΓÇõ `# type: ignore[call-overload]` ∞á£Ω▒░.  `router`, `signals`, `analyst`, `evaluator`, `scoring`, `skip_check`, `verification`, `synthesizer`, `gather` 9 δà╕δô£ δ¬¿δÀÉ.\n\n### Hardening Metrics\n- `# type: ignore` ∞┤ÙφòÒ: 53 ΓÁÈ **44** (active count, ΓêÈ9, ΓêÈ17 %)\n- `[call-overload]` ∞╣┤φàÔΩ│áδª¼: 13 ΓÁÈ 4 (graph.py 9 ΓÁÈ 0; tracing/tools/pipeline_executor 4 ∞₧õ∞í┤ ΓÇõ root-cause δÍñδÑ╕ SDK φò£Ω│ã)\n- pytest 4346 passed (δ│ÇδÂÕ ∞ùÁ∞ÙÔ); ruff/mypy clean (332 source files); E2E A (68.4) δÂÕ∞Ù╝."
