    "body": "Plan/Sub-agent NL integration, Claude Code-style UI, response quality hardening.\n\n### Added\n\n#### Plan & Sub-agent NL Integration\n- `create_plan` tool ΓÇõ NLδí£ δ╢ã∞ãÙ Ω│ãφÜì ∞âÙ∞ã▒ (\"Berserk δ╢ã∞ãÙ Ω│ãφÜì ∞ã╕∞¢Ô∞ñÌ\")\n- `approve_plan` tool ΓÇõ Ω│ãφÜì ∞è╣∞Ù╕ δ░Â ∞ÍñφÚÊ (\"Ω│ãφÜì ∞è╣∞Ù╕φò┤\")\n- `delegate_task` tool ΓÇõ ∞ã£δ╕Ô∞ùÉ∞Ù┤∞áãφè╕ δ│Àδá¼ ∞£ã∞₧ã (\"δ│Àδá¼δí£ ∞▓Ìδª¼φò┤\")\n- NL Router tool count: 17 ΓÁÈ 20 (plan/delegate 3Ω░£ ∞╢õΩ░Ç)\n- Offline fallback: plan/delegate regex φÔ¿φã┤ ∞╢õΩ░Ç (LLM ∞ùÁ∞Ù┤ δÂÕ∞₧À)\n\n#### Claude Code-style UI\n- `core/ui/agentic_ui.py` ΓÇõ tool call/result/error/token/plan δáÔδìõδÓ¼\n- `core/ui/console.py` ΓÇõ Rich Console ∞Í▒Ω╕ÇφÁñ (width=120, GEODE φàÔδºê)\n- Marker system: `ΓÚ╕` tool call, `Γ£ô` success, `Γ£ù` error, `Γ£ó` tokens, `ΓùÂ` plan\n\n#### LangSmith Trace Coverage\n- `@_maybe_traceable` added to verification layer: `run_guardrails`, `run_biasbuster`, `run_cross_llm_check`, `check_rights_risk`\n- Full pipeline tracing coverage: router ΓÁÈ signals ΓÁÈ analysts ΓÁÈ evaluators ΓÁÈ scoring ΓÁÈ verification ΓÁÈ synthesizer\n\n### Changed\n- `AgenticLoop._process_tool_calls()`: `str(result)` ΓÁÈ `json.dumps(result, ensure_ascii=False, default=str)` ΓÇõ LLM∞Ù┤ φÔÔ∞Í▒ Ω░ÇδèÑφò£ JSON φÌò∞ÍÙ∞£╝δí£ tool Ω▓░Ω│╝ ∞áãδÍ¼\n- `snapshot._persist_snapshot()`: `json.dumps(..., default=str)` ΓÇõ non-serializable φòãδô£ ∞òê∞áã ∞▓Ìδª¼\n- `snapshot.capture()`: `_sanitize_state()` ∞╢õΩ░Ç ΓÇõ `_`-prefixed δé┤δ╢Ç φòãδô£ φòãφã░δºü\n- NL Router offline fallback ∞ê£∞ã£: plan/delegate φÔ¿φã┤∞Ùã known IP δºñ∞╣¡δ│┤δÍñ δ¿╝∞áÇ Ω▓Ç∞é¼\n\n### Fixed\n- Offline mode `_run_offline()`: action name(\"list\") ΓÁÈ tool name(\"list_ips\") δºñφòÀ δêãδÙ╜ ∞êÌ∞áò (`_ACTION_TO_TOOL` dict ∞╢õΩ░Ç)\n- `_TOOL_ACTION_MAP` δêãδÙ╜: `create_plan`, `approve_plan`, `delegate_task` δ»╕δô▒δíÙ ΓÁÈ ∞╢õΩ░Ç\n\n### Infrastructure\n- Test count: 1909+ ΓÁÈ 2000+\n- Module count: 116 ΓÁÈ 118\n- `tests/test_agentic_ui.py` (20 tests), plan/delegate NL tests (20 tests)"
